                          <div class="it-about-2-text">
                              <p class="mb-30">Our school is committed to delivering high-quality education that nurtures intellectual curiosity, creativity, and lifelong learning. We provide students with the knowledge, confidence, and skills needed to succeed academically and personally.</p>
